item.title: When Footballing legend Pele awarded 7-time F1 Champion Michael Schumacher ahead of his final race with Ferrari
item.description: When Footballing legend Pele awarded 7-time F1 Champion Michael Schumacher ahead of his final race with Ferrari On the 22nd of October 2006, fans witnessed two of the greatest sportsmen of all time together on the centre stage, Brazilian Footballer Pele awarded Michael Schumacher the “Lifetime Achievement Award” for his tremendous career in F1.
